2026-05-14T00:31:55.9158807Z 220            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-14T00:31:55.9190061Z 221            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-14T00:31:55.9190896Z 222            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-14T00:31:55.9191670Z 223            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-14T00:31:55.9192542Z 224            ensures the activity is finished as soon as it leaves the
2026-05-14T00:31:55.9193400Z 225            foreground and is never re-entered with a missing extra. See
2026-05-14T00:31:55.9194280Z 226            crash report tagged "ProxyBillingActivity NPE" for context.
